about.summary: An interface to the Integrated Taxonomic Information System ('ITIS') (<https://www.itis.gov>). Includes functions to work with the 'ITIS' REST API methods (<https://www.itis.gov/ws_description.html>), as well as the 'Solr' web service (<https://www.itis.gov/solr_documentation.html>).

name: r-ritis
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.9.0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-ritis
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/ritis_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/ritis/ritis_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 4abbe6c860fd3e465116573c9b2f119dbbd0046646844551523188ded63f0f6c

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-crul >=0.4.0
    - r-data.table >=1.9.6
    - r-jsonlite >=1.5
    - r-solrium >=1.0.2
    - r-tibble >=1.3.4
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-crul >=0.4.0
    - r-data.table >=1.9.6
    - r-jsonlite >=1.5
    - r-solrium >=1.0.2
    - r-tibble >=1.3.4

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('ritis')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('ritis')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/ropensci/ritis
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: An interface to the Integrated Taxonomic Information System ('ITIS') (<https://www.itis.gov>). Includes functions to work with the 'ITIS' REST API methods
    (<https://www.itis.gov/ws_description.html>), as well as the 'Solr' web service (<https://www.itis.gov/solr_documentation.html>).
  license_family: MIT

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - ocefpaf
